[I] A set of convenient classes to use PipeWire in Qt projects

[T] KPipeWire is a KDE application or integration layer designed to interact
[T] with PipeWire multimedia framework. It acts as a bridge between KDE
[T] applications and the PipeWire framework.

[U] https://invent.kde.org/plasma/kpipewire

